'''''Chinese Democracy''''' is the name of the long-awaited sixth studio album by the hard rock band [[Guns N' Roses]]. When<!-- Don't change to "If released" --> released, it will be the band's first album of original studio material since the simultaneous release of ''[[Use Your Illusion I]]'' and ''[[Use Your Illusion II]]'' in [[1991]].

